  "prompt": "What is 3E - 3 tier AC in Duronto?",
  "response": "The term \"3E\" in the context of Indian Railways' Duronto trains refers to \"Third AC Economy,\" which is a class of travel that is a more economical version of the regular Third AC (3A) class. The 3E class offers air-conditioned travel with slightly fewer amenities compared to the standard Third AC class, generally at a lower fare. Duronto trains are known for their non-stop service between major cities, providing faster travel times.",
